main event: Two unidentified objects were observed on radar in close proximity on two separate occasions.
interesting points: The first sighting lasted for about 5 minutes with the objects alternating between straight and level flight paths., The second sighting showed one possibly two objects passing overhead at high speed., No metallic appearance or sound was noted during the second sighting., Both sightings had discrepancies between visual and radar observations., The investigations were limited due to military protocols and insufficient data for evaluation.
